    "brand_split_row_main": {
      "type": "brand-split-row",
      "name": "Image Text Split",
      "settings": {
        "width": "wrapper",
        "layout": "image-left",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/roberto-coin-cyprus.jpg",
        "text": "<p><strong>WHAT INSPIRED YOU TO TURN THAT APPRECIATION FOR BEAUTY INTO YOUR LIFE’S WORK?</strong></p><p>As a child, I spent every summer with my grandmother in the countryside near Venice. Every day I used to stop and look at a little workshop — Elsa’s Atelier. I saw how to create an object from a wish: how to sketch, how to choose fabrics, and about the harmony of colors and shapes. All of this inspired me deeply.</p><p>I fell in love with that world — and, being strong-minded, found a way to become part of it.</p>",
        "padding_top": 120,
